{"title":"绣幅壮锦上北京","authors":["黄德玉　韦立斌"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣幅壮锦上北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮族　黄德玉　韦立斌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪来天上最红的霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘下银河最亮的星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏作针虹作线啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣幅壮锦上北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先绣东方旭日升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席挥手指航程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再绣壮家革命人啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧跟统帅向前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花朵朵向阳开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心颗颗向着北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的恩情说不完啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮族人民的忠诚绣不尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金丝长哟情意深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣幅壮锦上北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给救星毛主席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表表壮族人民一片心。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}